The '''''Modaran''''' was an [[Assault shuttle/Legends|assault shuttle]] that was in service with the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]]. It participated in the [[First Battle of Borleias]]. During the battle, it and its [[Commander/Legends|commander]], [[General/Legends|General]] [[Laryn Kre'fey]], was destroyed when a barrage of [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]] fire disabled the transport, causing the ship to plummet into the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] renewed energy [[Deflector shield/Legends|shield]]. The ''Modaran'' was the first ship to be destroyed by [[Evir Derricote]]'s defenses during the battle.

==Behind the scenes==
In ''[[the Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]'' the name of the shuttle is listed as ''Mondaran'' but the spelling is correct in Laryn Kre'fey's entry.

